&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1700667/gabriel-c%c3%a2mara&quot; title=&quot;1,194 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Gabriel Cmara&lt;/a&gt;
